riction-upgrade_angled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062503/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_angled.jpg 1050w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062503/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_angled-297x226.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062503/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_angled-800x610.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062503/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_angled-120x91.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062503/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_angled-768x585.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062503/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_angled-696x530.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062503/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_angled-551x420.jpg 551w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062503/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_angled-80x60.jpg 80w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-265681\">all images c. absoluteBLACK</figcaption></figure><p>Obviously, everything here is new, so let’s look at the details that make it work. The “mono-plate” cage itself is made of “carbon-polymer” material, which sounds like the same high-performance carbon-reinforced composites we’ve seen from stiff shoe soles to Italian derailleur components.</p><p>It also gets a dimpled surface <em>à la</em> Zipp for improved aerodynamics. But absoluteBLACK says that a bit of flexibility in the cage is the secret here allowing the upper pulley to be perfectly placed for precise shift actuation while the lower pulley can more accurately twist to align towards the chainring for reduced friction</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062458/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_single-sided-cage-details.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062458/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_single-sided-cage-details.jpg\" alt=\"Absolute Black carbon-ceramic Hollow Cage low friction upgrade, angled details\" width=\"1050\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062458/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_single-sided-cage-details.jpg 1050w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062458/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_single-sided-cage-details-297x226.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062458/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_single-sided-cage-details-800x610.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062458/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_single-sided-cage-details-120x91.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062458/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_single-sided-cage-details-768x585.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062458/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-