g-detail-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062448/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_Xring-detail-800x500.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062448/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_Xring-detail-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062448/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_Xring-detail-768x480.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062448/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_Xring-detail-696x435.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062448/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_Xring-detail-1068x668.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19062448/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_Xring-detail-672x420.jpg 672w\"></a></p><p>Those tall teeth are also said to allow lower&nbsp;spring tension than any other cage on the market, without compromising shift precision. That means lower system friction and more watts-saved, still providing excellent shifting thanks to the unique combination of pulley stiffness and tall teeth profiles. In addition, it is the only cage that can dynamically adapt to the variable chainline, minimizing friction at the lower pulley.</p><h3>absoluteBLACK HOLLOWcage – Pricing, availability &amp; options</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/19061741/Absolute-Black-carbon-ceramic-Hollow-Cage-low-friction-upgrade_colors.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/u